### Hono Blog API - Test Requests
### Usage: Run with VS Code REST Client extension or similar

# ==================== AUTH ====================

### Register new user
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Login (get JWT token)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Extract token from login response
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Get current user profile
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ==================== PUBLIC POSTS ====================

### Get all posts
GET http://localhost:3001/api/posts

### Get all posts (page 2)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/posts?page=2

### Get single post by ID
GET http://localhost:3001/api/posts/48820de5-c4e0-4656-a8c0-7594288b67c6

# ==================== PROTECTED POSTS ====================

### Create new post
POST http://localhost:3001/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Новий пост",
  "content": "Контент нового посту"
}

### Update post (PATCH)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/posts/48820de5-c4e0-4656-a8c0-7594288b67c6
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Оновлений заголовок",
  "content": "Оновлений контент посту"
}

### Delete post
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/posts/9ee2fee9-220e-45ec-bebb-5140c60b8145
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get author's own posts
GET http://localhost:3001/api/my/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ==================== COMMENTS ====================

### Get comments for a post
GET http://localhost:3001/api/posts/48820de5-c4e0-4656-a8c0-7594288b67c6/comments

### Create new comment
POST http://localhost:3001/api/posts/48820de5-c4e0-4656-a8c0-7594288b67c6/comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "Новий коментар до посту"
}

### Update comment (PATCH)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/posts/48820de5-c4e0-4656-a8c0-7594288b67c6/comments/16ef6d76-f1ec-4ee9-9106-dbf614846c3d
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "Оновлений текст коментаря"
}

### Delete comment
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/posts/48820de5-c4e0-4656-a8c0-7594288b67c6/comments/ae4236d1-9938-402c-8478-40bd8cf74159
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get author's own comments
GET http://localhost:3001/api/my/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ==================== ERROR CASES ====================

### Try to create post without auth (should fail 401)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "No auth post",
  "content": "This should fail"
}

### Try to update someone else's post (should fail 404)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/posts/some-other-uuid
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Hacked title",
  "content": "This should fail"
}

### Invalid token (should fail 401)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/my/posts
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token-here

### Validation error - empty title (should fail 400)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "",
  "content": "Some content"
}

### Validation error - missing fields (should fail 400)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": "123"
}
